Package play.data.parsing

Class Summary
ApacheMultipartParser From Apache commons fileupload.
DataParser A data parser parse the HTTP request data to a Map
JsonParser JSON Parser
MultipartStream Low level API for processing file uploads.
TempFilePlugin Creates temporary folders for file parsing, and deletes it after request completion.
UrlEncodedParser Parse url-encoded requests.
 

Exception Summary
ApacheMultipartParser.SizeException This exception is thrown, if a requests permitted size is exceeded.
MultipartStream.IllegalBoundaryException Thrown upon attempt of setting an invalid boundary token.
MultipartStream.MalformedStreamException Thrown to indicate that the input stream fails to follow the required syntax.
